00:24.182 --> 00:26.706
Wrapped him in cloth and laid him in a manger.

00:31.650 --> 00:36.836
In the same region, shepherds were staying out in the field at night and keeping watch over their flock.

00:37.496 --> 00:43.443
Then an angel of the Lord stood before them, and the glory of the Lord shone around them.

00:44.304 --> 00:53.794
But the angel said to them, Do not be afraid, for I proclaim to you good news of great joy that will be for all the people.

00:53.814 --> 00:56.917
Today in the city of David, a Savior was born.

00:57.979 --> 01:01.202
For you who is the Messiah, the Lord,

01:19.746 --> 01:23.070
Good evening, everybody.

01:24.292 --> 01:42.936
So has anyone ever looked at the world, like through watching the news scrolling through, especially scrolling through social media, and just thought to themselves like, man, this world is crazy.

01:45.439 --> 01:47.442
Yeah, right.

01:47.682 --> 01:53.331
I know a weird way to start a Christmas Eve message, but I know I can't be the only one.

01:53.351 --> 01:57.437
