02:39.908 --> 02:41.810
Now I know it's not me,

02:41.986 --> 02:50.194
any of my skills, which aren't many, or anything that I can do that makes the gospel penetrate the hearts of those who listen to it.

02:50.214 --> 02:58.382
I know it's our God, but still, it can be overwhelming at times with this task.

02:59.603 --> 03:06.150
