that he lays down his life for his friends, and that's exactly what Jesus did for you.

20:16.014 --> 20:18.477
Number two, there's room for you in this family.

20:19.579 --> 20:26.128
The Bible says, but to all who did receive him, he gave them the right to become children of God.

